text: Alexandru Cătălin Mica (; born 25 August 1991), known as Alex Mica, is a Romanian dance/pop music singer. Mica's song "Dalinda" placed on the Bulgaria Top 20 chart for three weeks in May–June 2012.http://top40-charts.com/song.php?sid=33706 For this song, he won Best New Act at that year's Romanian Music Awards.
